value.string: Sch Person Property Flag Check BOT
To Validate scheduled personal property contains Y or Not.
1.Capture text from the policy endorsement screen.
2. Store all induvidual values into the list.
3. Iterate each elements of the  list and find for HO 04 61 and check wether it contains Y or Not and assign it to varFlag.
4. If H0 04 61 is not present then it throws Error "HO 0461 Property Not Found"

value.expression: This is after extracting substring op -  $varFlag$
